alert-message:
Congratulations! You just indicated that you have completed all of the modules in the [pathway] pathway!

While we won't be sending you regular emails about your progress, you will always have access to the modules in your pathway, which is displayed at the end of this email for your future reference. You are also welcome to check out the complete collection of modules in the DART program.

Congratulations again on your acheivement!

The entire DART team

Welcome
Reproducibility, Generalizability, and Reuse 60 min
Learn R
R Basics: Introduction 60 min
R Basics: Visualizing Data With ggplot2 60 min
R Basics: Transforming Data With dplyr 60 min
Missing Values in R 45 min
Tidy Data 45 min
Reshaping Data in R: Long and Wide Data 60 min
Summary Statistics in R 30 min
R Practice 1 hour
Statistics and Machine Learning
Introduction to Null Hypothesis Significance Testing 40 min
Statistical Tests in Open Source Software 20 min
Demystifying Machine Learning 60 min
Understanding the Bias-Variance Tradeoff 20 min
Databases
Demystifying SQL 40 min
SQL Basics 1 hour
SQL, Intermediate Level 60 min
Database Normalization 40 min
SQL Joins 1 hour
Learn Python
Python Basics: Variables, Functions, and Methods 20 min
Python Basics: Lists and Dictionaries 15 min
Python Basics: Loops and Conditionals 20 min
Python Basics: Exercise 30 min
Transform Data with pandas 1 hour
Data Visualization in seaborn 60 min
Python Practice 1 hour

email-subject: Log back in and keep learning!
alert-message:
Hi!

We noticed that it has been a while since you logged any progress in your DART Program learning pathway:

[survey-link:magnolia_pathway][new-instance]

This link will take you to a page with the full list of education modules curated for you by our team. Indicate which ones you've been working on, and click Submit at the bottom of the form to log your progress. You can update your progress as many times as you want, either by following the link in this email, or by pasting the following url into your browser:

[survey-url:magnolia_pathway][new-instance] This link is unique to you and should not be forwarded to others.

Log in today to try out the next module in your learning pathway!

We look forward to seeing you on the platform, and please don't hesitate to email us if you have any technical (or other) questions.

Sincerely,

The DART Team at Children's Hospital of Philadelphia

P.S. If you have decided that participating in the DART program isn't for you after all, reply to this email to let us know and we will unenroll you from the study.
